  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK879">
<l>iḷaitāka muṇmaraṅ kolka kaḷaiyunar </l>
<l>kaikolluṅ kāḻtta viṭattu</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>A thorny tree should be felled while young, (for) when it is grown it will destroy the hand of the feller.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
